<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,1045,2006]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1045,1070]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Easily distinguished from similar congeners (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Huber" authorityYear="2018" box="[818,952,1046,1069]" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Mesabolivar" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acrensis">
<emphasis box="[818,952,1046,1069]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">M. acrensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Huber" authorityYear="2018" box="[971,1100,1045,1070]" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Mesabolivar" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maraba">
<emphasis box="[971,1100,1045,1070]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">M. maraba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Gonzalez-Sponga" authorityYear="1998" box="[1119,1387,1045,1070]" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Mesabolivar" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pseudoblechroscelis">
<emphasis box="[1119,1387,1045,1070]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">M. pseudoblechroscelis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) by screw-shaped sclerite prolaterally on bulbal process (
<figureCitation box="[785,923,1081,1106]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–31" captionStartId="13.[151,264,1939,1961]" captionTargetBox="[151,1432,553,1911]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[151,1436,553,1917]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURES 26–31. Mesabolivar huambisa Huber, 2000. Left procursi, retrolateral views, and left bulbal processes, prolateral views; from Samiria (type locality) (26, 29, MUSM), Tabatinga (27, 30, ZFMK Ar 18950), and Belém (28, 31, ZFMK Ar 18951).Arrow points at distinctive screw-shaped sclerite.Scale lines:0.5 (26–28), 0.3 (29–31)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202527/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Figs 29–31</figureCitation>
); also by shape of procursus (
<figureCitation box="[1295,1432,1081,1106]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–31" captionStartId="13.[151,264,1939,1961]" captionTargetBox="[151,1432,553,1911]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[151,1436,553,1917]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURES 26–31. Mesabolivar huambisa Huber, 2000. Left procursi, retrolateral views, and left bulbal processes, prolateral views; from Samiria (type locality) (26, 29, MUSM), Tabatinga (27, 30, ZFMK Ar 18950), and Belém (28, 31, ZFMK Ar 18951).Arrow points at distinctive screw-shaped sclerite.Scale lines:0.5 (26–28), 0.3 (29–31)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202527/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Figs 26–28</figureCitation>
; distinctive distal elements) and by shape of epigynum (
<figureCitation box="[770,901,1117,1142]" captionStart="FIGURES 32–47" captionStartId="14.[151,264,1829,1851]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1808]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[151,1436,193,1808]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURES 32–47. Female epigyna in ventral and lateral views and cleared female genitalia, dorsal views, Mesabolivar pseudoblechroscelisgroup (part 1). 32–38. M. acrensissp. n., from Rio Branco (32–33, 38, ZFMK Ar 18943), Cruzeirodo Sul (34–37, ZFMK Ar 18946). 39–41. M. maraba sp. n. (ZFMK Ar 18948). 42–47. M. huambisa Huber, 2000, from Samiria (42– 43, MUSM), Tabatinga (44–45, ZFMK Ar 18950), and Belém (46–47, ZFMK Ar 18951)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202529/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Figs 42–47</figureCitation>
; median cavity very wide, not reaching anterior epigynal margin; lateral pair of processes directed towards ventral) (female of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Gonzalez-Sponga" authorityYear="1998" box="[1029,1293,1153,1178]" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Mesabolivar" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pseudoblechroscelis">
<emphasis box="[1029,1293,1153,1178]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">M. pseudoblechroscelis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
unknown).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
